  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Rigor Declaration">
      Output: 🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL · 📋 REASON: code-impl in BFF; deletion tag; modifies orchestrator hot path + tests; ADR-038 TEST-MODIFYING override applies (FULL rigor unconditional); quality gates Step 9.5 required · Proceeding with Step 0...
