    <step order="9.5" name="Quality gates (FULL rigor)">
      Run `/code-review` on the diff — focus on missed call sites + appropriate test deletions per ADR-038.
      Run `/adr-check` against ADR-029 + ADR-038 + bff-extensions.md.
      Fix any findings.
    </step>
    <step order="10" name="Update current-task.md + TASK-INDEX">
